'''Leisuretowne''' is a [[census-designated place]] and [[unincorporated area (New Jersey)|unincorporated area]] located within [[Southampton Township, New Jersey|Southampton Township]], in [[Burlington County, New Jersey|Burlington County]], [[New Jersey]]. As of the [[United States 2000 census]], the CDP population was 2,535. Nearly 80% of the CDPs residents are 65 years of age or older.

==Geography==
Leisuretowne is located at {{coord|39.900120|-74.706284|type:city_region:US|format=dms|display=inline}} (39.900120, -74.706284).{{GR|1}}

According to the [[United States Census Bureau]], the CDP has a total area of 4.8&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> (1.9 mi<sup>2</sup>). 4.6&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> (1.8 mi<sup>2</sup>) of it is land and 0.2&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> (0.1 mi<sup>2</sup>) of it (4.81%) is water.

==Demographics==
